{"tid":1634331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter / Reddit 要人啊！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:31:24.000Z","uid":31581,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"edfcf58b65bde256e1e2411601aafa1923d1926a","tid":1634331,"uid":31581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"Twitter / Reddit 要人！<br />\n<br />\n大家除左本地戰線（fb/連登）外, 國際輿論/新聞戰（Twitter/Reddit)都好需要關注同出一分力！呢場已經係一場世界參與既抗爭, 需要香港每個人都係Twitter/ Reddit 發出聲音, 你可以post每日警暴既相/片, 可以comment暴政既新聞等等, 就係需要你既活躍！<br />\n<br />\nTwitter入門: join <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=cbd999fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n入面有每日任務, 主要係將admin每日推介既post retweet w/ comment + like + hashtag, 需要有30k以上既tweet就有機會推上國際層面<br />\n<br />\nReddit入門：你當係海外連登 （呢個係超級需要人同花心機時間！）<br />\nJoin <a href=\"http://t.me/redditmansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fredditmansyunzou&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=2bebe3ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/redditmansyunzou</a><br />\nReddit有好多subcom, 揀主流去join先（睇pin), comment + upvote admin推介post. Reddit係一個好睇你俾幾多input既地方, 亦好睇你有幾多Karma, Kamra就係impact factor, 你俾得愈多高質comment, 你Karma愈高, 你既post先愈易上到國際舞台.<br />\n<br />\nTroubleshooting: <br />\nQ: 我英文好廢，玩唔到😔<br />\nA: 英文唔一定非常好，bottom line係你睇得明人地寫咩，你又寫得出人地明既英文就得，我地係想人關注我地，所以你表達到自己就足夠。另外，大部份情況係你愈玩，英文變得愈好<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我可否瘋狂copy &amp; paste comment同hashtag?<br />\nA: Twitter都可以, 但Reddit一定唔得, 佢好似連登咁有機制filter走垃圾式推post. 所以你要學三毛咁四圍俾啲有內容，係有內容，係有內容既comment咁先可以儲到Karma<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁花時間，已經好攰，我唔玩啦<br />\nA: 停低休息一下. 呢4個月黎辛苦大家🙇🏻&zwj;♂️ 冇群眾既努力實在唔會走到今日. 你可能覺得咁做好左膠, 但我每日只要諗到成場運動犧牲左咁多人命, 成千幾人被捕, 我唔想對唔住佢地. 希望大家一齊開闢新戰線, 令運動更走向國際。"},{"pid":"1725bc986065488568ee390abdb78d8ffdc08bbe","tid":1634331,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=0d8d3617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=db4f35fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com/</a>"},{"pid":"51df0f204ccbef5ffaf225e26a9fdf0b82f01d71","tid":1634331,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=0d8d3617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=db4f35fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com/</a>"},{"pid":"8c71a4a5bf3d790cfbf9eb16cde197be81b3e8bc","tid":1634331,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=0d8d3617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=db4f35fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com/</a>"},{"pid":"00476740e653ce56c3430ca6f45